• Tech stack: Python3, Django, Heroku, Firebase, React, jQuery;

• Team composition: 1 Back-end dev, 1 Front-end dev, 1 Android dev, 1 AI dev, PM;

• WH - 9am-6pm GMT+7;

• Office attendance;

